Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:08.08,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121913,128086}Tsukikage Theater and its rival,\NOndine Theater, did the same play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.08,0:02:12.42,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:128086,132424}Maya created her own way of playing\Nthe main role, opposite from that of Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:132424,140140}…which led to both teams winning\Nand advancing to the National Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:27.14,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141099,147147}{\an5\pos(766,750)\fscy95\blur1\fad(800,0)}—Episode 06—\NThe Trap of the National Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:38.24,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:152903,158241}As spring came, Maya and her crew\Nhave departed to Nagoya for the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:44.03,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:158241,164039}Tsukikage Theater will play a fairy tale-like\Nsuspense, "Gena and the Five Blue Pots."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:46.58,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:164039,166583}Maya will again play the main role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:51.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166583,171004}I bet there will be really competitive\Nteams from all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173548,177260}I haven't seen Sakurakōji for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177260,178845}I wonder if I'll get to see him in Nagoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180639,181890}Here, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181890,182808}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182808,185102}Maya. Ms. Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185102,185811}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188021,190148}Oh, shoot, you guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192526,193358}Look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193358,197614}Acting like she's on top of the world\Nafter playing the main role in the past two plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197614,200033}Yeah. It's partly Miss Tsukikage's fault too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200033,203203}Using us only as supporting roles for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203203,204538}But watch, she will soon see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211837,214506}You must be tired after a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214506,218218}Teams that stay in our inn usually have good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218218,220053}So I wish you the best luck for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.38,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:220053,222389}– Thank you.\N– All right then, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226393,229020}Oh no, there's a cemetery\Nright outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229020,230355}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230355,232190}You can see the shrine on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232190,234151}Kind of spooky, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234151,237112}I don't like this kind of atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237112,239156}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239698,241241}Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242159,243326}Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259176,260385}What's that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260385,261720}It's coming from the graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261720,262637}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262637,263638}Wolves?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263638,265265}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309851,312187}What do you guys want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312187,313939}O-Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313939,316149}We were wondering\Nwhat you guys were doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316149,317609}What we are doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317609,319110}Acting practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319110,320111}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320111,322197}This is acting practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322197,323740}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323740,326243}We practice acting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326243,327202}But this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327202,329079}You practice acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329913,332040}Well, you are interrupting our practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339256,342008}Look! The guys from last night\Nare in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342008,343301}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:47.26,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:343301,347264}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344052,347889}Ikkakuju, a drama team from Hokkaidō,\Nis aiming in a new direction of acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.80,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:347889,348807}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348807,351476}It says they are one of the winning\Ncandidates of the acting contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351476,356439}The heads-up favorite along\Nwith Ondine Theater for winning the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356439,358692}It was a different style of acting from ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358692,360193}But they sure were powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:01.19,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:360193,361194}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362112,366157}If we don't win this contest,\Nthen it's over for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369911,373123}This is Tsukikage Theater.\NWe're here for a rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373123,374499}Hold on just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374499,376209}The other group is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376209,378628}We can't go in there right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379129,381756}No, sir. We don't let\Nanyone in during rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381756,384092}I've never heard of anything like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384092,386177}Look, they even have security?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386177,387846}I wonder which team they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389097,391600}We've just finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391600,392851}Pull the car up in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392851,393602}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393602,394394}That's Ondine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394394,397480}I heard they are going\Nthrough a hard training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397480,399774}They'll play a serious drama,\N"The Castle of Ashes."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.98,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:400901,401985}Door 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405864,406948}Ms. Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406948,407823}Look…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407823,410243}She's lost so much weight,\Nshe doesn't even look the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414247,415373}How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415373,419336}Despite all the weight loss, she looks\Neven more beautiful and confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424299,425175}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427177,428470}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428469,429846}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429846,432933}You must be tired,\Nso please don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432933,434142}Sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436311,437062}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452410,453995}Maya, we'll be in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454913,456665}Sakurakōji…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456665,458291}I finally got to see you, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463880,465131}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465131,466591}Ah, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466591,468009}The training is about to start downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471346,474432}That's right. I have to concentrate\Nonly on acting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.35,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:475767,478353}The National Contest finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.81,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:478353,480813}The best troupes from all over the country…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:04.35,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:480813,484359}…are about to compete\Nwith each other for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:04.35,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:479396,484359}Japan National Acting Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487529,489656}Hurry up, Maya!\NThe seats will be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489656,490573}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493201,494244}Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494244,495078}Doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495912,496538}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497455,499499}We finally got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:25.25,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502127,505255}I have to ask.\NI have to ask him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508091,509801}S-Sakurakōji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509801,513054}You must be really close with Ms. Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513054,514555}Oh? Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517475,518559}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519436,524858}I thought all you cared about\Nwas acting and didn't even notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524858,528653}But I'm glad that you are\Nthinking of me like that. I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529529,531156}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531156,535952}Let's be good friends, no matter what happens\Nbetween Ondine and Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535952,536661}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545670,549466}Since you were so late, all the seats\Nwere taken while we were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549466,551593}Yeah, we ended up standing in the isle like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551593,554637}I'm really sorry.\NIt's just that…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554637,557724}Look at this girl!\NShe's laughing trying to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558391,560268}Hey, look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560268,562937}So uppity, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562937,564606}Yeah. Who do they think they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564606,566816}No courtesy to us older ones at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566816,567942}Did anything good happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567942,568693}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568693,569778}Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569778,572113}Can I have a talk with you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.45,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:578328,581456}The contest progressed without any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:48.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:584375,588379}The Castle of Ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:47.25,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:584584,587252}Most of all, "The Castle of Ashes"\Nby Ondine Theater…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.09,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:587252,590090}…was praised highly by the audience\Nfor its emotional parts…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:55.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:590090,595845}…whereas Ayumi, who played\Na proud princess, was admired to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:22.53,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:615782,622539}Ikkakuju Theater's different\Nand energized play, "Destiny…"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:28.04,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:622539,628044}…energized the audience so much\Nthat they were requested for an encore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642851,645228}That's all.\NThis is all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645228,647772}Please deliver this to the theater by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647772,648648}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648648,650066}It's finally the day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650066,650817}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651776,653278}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653278,655613}I'll play the best Gena I can.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:11.67,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671671,671671}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:15.55,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:675550,675550}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:18.55,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:678553,678553}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693693,695195}Fresh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695570,696988}Hey, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696988,697488}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699532,700742}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717508,719427}How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:719427,721804}All of our equipment\Nand costumes are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721804,723555}Who in the world did this, and why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723555,727685}We found all this while jogging here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727685,729646}Maya's costume is still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730438,732190}But that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732190,736319}Even if Maya's costume is still intact,\Neverything else is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737862,739697}There's no way we can play now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741949,744160}I think they did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744160,745078}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745078,746204}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746204,749749}Criminals often act as if they found it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.62,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:749749,751626}– He has a point.\N– I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752293,755338}That's a lie! There's no way\Nwe would do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755338,756798}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756798,759550}Don't blame without any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759550,761344}But, Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761344,763471}What the…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763471,765098}Is there any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765098,768184}Well, there's no evidence\Nthat you are not the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768184,769477}That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:12.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791874,792750}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804887,805805}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805805,806597}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807598,808598}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814188,817233}Alright, help Maya fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817233,820820}We don't have time\Nto be blaming people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820820,822739}Yes, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822739,824407}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824407,828161}If we all try, then we can fix it\Nby our play at 2 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828161,829329}Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829329,832081}That's right.\NWe don't have time to blame anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832081,834625}Here, we'll give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835960,838379}Yes, we can swear we didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838379,841257}We'll help you to clear this allegation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841257,843217}For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843217,847972}Most of all, I heard\Nyou played as good as Ondine did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847972,849098}I want to see your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851059,853853}Leave it up to me.\NI'm used to putting these together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853853,855604}Thank you. We appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855604,857148}I'll go get the tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857148,858149}Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858149,859650}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868785,870453}Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870453,871871}Oh, the lady from the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871871,874957}Everyone, we can rent\Nequipment and costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.58,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:874957,875583}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876709,878294}Equipment and costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878294,886094}Yes. My nephew is an acting teacher\Nat a high school about an hour away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886094,887720}Acting club at a high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887720,893476}I called him just for the slightest possibility,\Nand they have everything you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895937,898940}Oh my gosh. I can play Gena now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902235,904612}An hour drive from here…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904612,908366}We can leave right now and size our costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908366,910868}Teacher, please let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910868,913329}We have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919877,921379}Hey, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921379,922839}Do you even need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922839,925132}We have to think of something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937979,939905}I know you are on your way back from work…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939905,943276}…but are you really into this business\Nof checking their play out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943276,946779}I'm confident that Ondine will win\Nafter watching "The Castle of Ashes."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946779,949115}But I still want to see the play by our rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950241,951576}"Rival?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952618,954078}"Rival," huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970511,972180}Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972180,974390}I heard all their equipment was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974390,975516}Destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986194,988029}I wonder if Onodera was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007673,1009467}My god, how dusty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009467,1011302}But we can use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011302,1013679}Please take as much as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013679,1015515}I hope I can be of some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015515,1016390}You are a big help to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016390,1017808}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024524,1026901}Whoa, this is a little too tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026901,1028653}Don't complain now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032698,1034909}It's 11:30 already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034909,1037119}The equipment's all fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037119,1039205}Now we just have to wait for them to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045253,1046837}I hope it doesn't get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058641,1061226}Hey, are you serious?\NAre we really going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061226,1061769}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.23,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063688,1067233}It's nice to hear\Nthat you would do anything for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.44,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067233,1068442}Please tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.02,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068442,1071028}We'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.82,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071028,1073823}Well, you guys are so talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.20,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073823,1076200}If you join Ondine,\Nyou will be casted right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.57,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076200,1077577}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.66,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077577,1080663}Yes. But to do so…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:05.58,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080663,1085585}…you have to show that you\Ndon't have any ties to Tsukikage Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:13.88,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089755,1093884}Like keeping them from entering the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.67,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093884,1094677}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:19.55,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096137,1099557}I just want you to show me some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104645,1105896}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105896,1107896}Something's wrong with the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113404,1115197}Do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117033,1118784}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118784,1120244}Engine trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120244,1122038}Yeah, I used to work as a mechanic before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122038,1125166}I'll try fixing it as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125166,1126500}We'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126500,1128878}Please, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130588,1132423}Why does the truck have to break down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134008,1135592}Something's strange here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140139,1141515}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141515,1143059}They should have been here a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148939,1150524}Please start getting ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150524,1153986}This play should be over by 1:40 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153986,1154945}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155946,1157490}Please hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157990,1159533}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159533,1161952}I wonder if they are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172004,1173005}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173005,1174423}You can't fix it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174423,1175341}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175341,1178094}It's more complicated than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178094,1179053}We're not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181555,1183224}There's no way we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189855,1190690}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190690,1194902}Rei, Sayaka, everyone… come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194902,1196153}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196153,1197071}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197071,1198989}The stage set is not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198989,1202743}That's a problem. You have\Nto set it up as soon as this play is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206205,1207748}The play just got done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208582,1210126}Twenty minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210126,1211460}Please come back…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212712,1214588}Rei, Sayaka…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214588,1215548}Everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:16.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215548,1216549}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224014,1225641}Why don't you get back inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225641,1227017}You'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227017,1228185}Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228728,1230811}I want to wait here till they get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231731,1234525}I don't understand why this is happening to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234525,1237945}We practiced so hard for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237945,1239530}Come on, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239530,1240406}You are soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241824,1243117}Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244493,1246787}I know you are having fun seeing us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246787,1249206}You wished that we won't be able to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259133,1260551}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260551,1262094}You're totally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264847,1267558}It's always better to have fewer rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267558,1270478}You guys especially should be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276317,1277401}Terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277401,1278861}What a terrible thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294001,1296045}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296045,1298130}…will never…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298130,1299632}…ever forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310810,1312895}Look at me. I'm Hayami Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314438,1318442}The president of Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319819,1322321}And I'm all soaking wet for this little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328160,1329328}Don't kid me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329328,1332289}You won't be able to make it on time\Nif you don't start setting up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332289,1333707}You don't have your actors yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333707,1335751}I have no choice but to call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337253,1341131}If they don't show up by 2 PM,\Nthen you will be forced to withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341131,1342049}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1342049,1343092}Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:24.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343092,1344301}Withdraw?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:33.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352685,1353727}Please come back…
